title: Lunchbox And Eddie Take On 'Lemon Juice Challenge' + Raymundo Rejects Mom’s Wedding Request +  Summer ‘Mixtapes'
itunes:title: Lunchbox And Eddie Take On 'Lemon Juice Challenge' + Raymundo Rejects Mom’s Wedding Request +  Summer ‘Mixtapes'
description:
Lunchbox and Eddie try and drink one liter of lemon juice in under 25 seconds. If they do, one of them wins a prize! Raymundo explains why he rejected his mom’s wedding dance song request. Plus, Bobby, Amy and Eddie share what songs would be on their 2020 summer mixtape!
